    "markdown": "---\ntitle: \"Current Fuel Prices — US Map\"\nsubtitle: \"PADD-region retail gasoline, most recent weekly snapshot\"\n---\n\n\n\n::: {.callout-note appearance=\"simple\"}\nRetail regular gasoline by **PADD region** (Petroleum Administration for\nDefense District). Each state is shaded by its PADD's weekly price.\nSource: EIA weekly retail-price survey. Cadence: weekly.\n:::\n\n## Current PADD retail gasoline {#map}\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n::: {.cell-output-display}\n\n```{=html}\n<div class=\"plotly html-widget html-fill-item\" id=\"htmlwidget-89e4944a313c1b114420\" style=\"width:100%;height:325px;\"></div>\n<script type=\"application/json\" data-for=\"htmlwidget-89e4944a313c1b114420\">{\"x\":{\"visdat\":{\"b6265a2c0316\":[\"function () \",\"plotlyVisDat\"]},\"cur_data\":\"b6265a2c0316\",\"attrs\":{\"b6265a2c0316\":{\"locationmode\":\"USA-states\",\"locations\":{},\"z\":{},\"text\":{},\"hoverinfo\":\"text\",\"colorscale\":[[\"0\",\"#2f9e44\"],[\"0.5\",\"#fcbf49\"],[\"1\",\"#bc4749\"]],\"colorbar\":{\"title\":\"$/gal\",\"tickformat\":\".2f\"},\"alpha_stroke\":1,\"sizes\":[10,100],\"spans\":[1,20],\"type\":\"choropleth\"}},\"layout\":{\"margin\":{\"b\":40,\"l\":60,\"t\":25,\"r\":10},\"title\":{\"text\":\"Retail regular gasoline by PADD region — April 2026\",\"x\":0.5,\"xanchor\":\"center\"},\"geo\":{\"scope\":\"usa\",\"projection\":{\"type\":\"albers usa\"},\"showlakes\":true,\"lakecolor\":\"#ffffff\"},\"scene\":{\"zaxis\":{\"title\":\"price\"}},\"hovermode\":\"closest\",\"showlegend\":false,\"legend\":{\"yanchor\":\"top\",\"y\":0.5}},\"source\":\"A\",\"config\":{\"modeBarButtonsToAdd\":[\"hoverclosest\",\"hovercompare\"],\"showSendToCloud\":false,\"displayModeBar\":false},\"data\":[{\"colorbar\":{\"title\":\"$/gal\",\"ticklen\":2,\"tickformat\":\".2f\",\"len\":0.5,\"lenmode\":\"fraction\",\"y\":1,\"yanchor\":\"top\"},\"colorscale\":[[\"0\",\"#2f9e44\"],[\"0.5\",\"#fcbf49\"],[\"1\",\"#bc4749\"]],\"showscale\":true,\"locationmode\":\"USA-states\",\"locations