600},{\"color\":\"#bc4749\",\"fontWeight\":600},{\"color\":\"#2f9e44\",\"fontWeight\":600}]}],\"defaultSorted\":[{\"id\":\"current\",\"desc\":true}],\"highlight\":true,\"striped\":true,\"compact\":true,\"theme\":{\"borderColor\":\"#dee2e6\"},\"dataKey\":\"b464a7a222a0821881946c7befddea11\"},\"children\":[]},\"class\":\"reactR_markup\"},\"evals\":[],\"jsHooks\":[]}</script>\n```\n\n:::\n:::\n\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n:::\n\n\n## Why PADD and not state?\n\nEIA publishes weekly retail gasoline at the **5 PADD regions**\ncomprehensively. State-level weekly coverage exists for only ~10 states.\nFor a complete national picture without geographic holes, PADD aggregation\nis the honest choice. Every state in a PADD shares the same color because\nthey share the same weekly aggregate.\n",
